  "Description": {
    "English": "A solemn power radiates from this ancient carving. Though the imagery is simple and the rendering rough, the meaning of the glyph has mathematical precision.<br><br>The glyph <span class=\"name name-special\">burns</span> with a resonant energy in the presence of <span class=\"name name-special\">Atlantideum</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这古老的雕刻散发着庄严的力量，尽管图像简单，形式朴素，但符文的含义却有着数学的精度。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-special\">亚特拉迪姆</span>的影响喜爱，符文<span class=\"name name-special\">燃烧</span>起了共鸣的能量",
    "TraditionalChinese": "古老雕刻散發出莊嚴的力量。雖然意象簡單、手法粗糙，表達出的符號含意卻有著數學般的精確度。<br><br>符號因<span class=\"name name-special\">亞特蘭提德鋼</span>的共振能量而<span class=\"name name-special\">熊熊燃燒</span>"
  },
